# VoiceVault тАФ General Project Conventions

## Project Overview

**VoiceVault** is an open-source **cross-platform desktop app** that records, transcribes, summarizes, and auto-organizes voice recordings into structured notes тАФ **all on-device, no server required**.

**Tech Stack:**
- **Electron** (v40+) тАФ Desktop app shell
- **React 19** тАФ UI framework with functional components only
- **TypeScript 5+** тАФ Strict mode, no `any`
- **electron-vite** тАФ Build tooling (Vite-based, fast HMR)
- **electron-forge** тАФ Packaging & distribution (DMG/deb/exe)
- **pnpm** тАФ Package manager (NOT npm or yarn)
- **Tailwind CSS v4** тАФ Utility-first styling
- **shadcn/ui** тАФ Accessible UI primitives (Radix-based)
- **react-i18next** тАФ i18n (Korean primary, English/Japanese support)

**Target Platforms:** macOS (Apple Silicon optimized with CoreML), Linux, Windows

**Repository:** https://github.com/PJH720/VoiceVault

