## Build Commands

### Prerequisites
- **Node.js** 20+ (LTS recommended)
- **pnpm** 9+ (install via `npm install -g pnpm`)
- ~5 GB free disk space (for AI models)
- macOS 13+ / Linux / Windows 10+

### Quick Start
```bash
git clone https://github.com/PJH720/VoiceVault.git
cd VoiceVault
pnpm install
pnpm dev
```

### Available Scripts
| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `pnpm dev` | Start in development mode with hot reload (Vite HMR) |
| `pnpm build` | Build for production (minified, tree-shaken) |
| `pnpm package` | Package the app (unsigned) |
| `pnpm make` | Package + create distributable (DMG/deb/exe) |
| `pnpm lint` | ESLint + TypeScript check |
| `pnpm lint:fix` | Auto-fix linting issues |
| `pnpm test` | Run Vitest unit tests |
| `pnpm test:watch` | Unit tests in watch mode |
| `pnpm test:e2e` | Run Playwright E2E tests |
| `pnpm test:coverage` | Generate test coverage report |
| `pnpm typecheck` | TypeScript type checking (all processes) |

